result.name: Mr. Park Korean Restaurant

reviews.text: Enjoy Korean cuisine, enjoy Mr Park’s hospitality!  Have come here like three times, each and every time was warmly greeted by Mr Park.  You can trust his recommendations.  The food was so good.  Just good food, no fancy drinks.  My only concern is, it’s a bit pricey.
Korean delicious restaurant with friendly serving

Mr. Park serves his food with the freshest ingredients and couples it with friendly company. His home-cooked meals for his customers brings people on an emotional, flavourful ride to South Korea. I love it here!
Good korean food

Now my favorite korean restaurants in hong kong!!!! I really injoyed the food especially a sliced Beef Rib hehe 
they served a variety of side dishes and also staff was really nice!
